hland Ave. south to Roosevelt Road; the go east on Roosevelt to Maxwell; turn south on Maxwell.  From the South: Take the Dan Ryan Expressway (I-90/94) and exit on Roosevelt Road (1200 south); go west on Roosevelt Road to Maxwell Street; then turn south on Maxwell.  From the West: Take the Eisenhower Expressway (I-290) to the Ashland Avenue exit; take Ashland Avenue south to Roosevelt Rd; then go east on Roosevelt to Maxwell, turn right on Maxwell.  From the East: Take Roosevelt Road west to Maxwell Street; turn south on Maxwell.          Bike Rack Locations   Campus map with bicycle rack locations  1) Select the layers view   2) Select Bike Rack Locations           Contact    Back to main content           Get a Report    Maps & Directions    Phone Numbers                   UIC Logo         University  Police           Locations    Springfield    Urbana-Champaign    Regional Campuses      Related Links    Office of the Vice Chancellor of Administrative Services    Office of Preparedness and Response    Housing    Office of Access and Equity    Campus Advocacy Network    Dean of Students    Transportation Services    Parking         Contact   943 West Maxwell Street, MC 268, Chicago, IL 60608-1563  Phone: Emergency:  (312) 355-5555 | General: (312) 996-2830  uicpd@uic.edu        Social Media Accounts             UIC.edu links   UIC.edu  Academic Calendar  Athletics  Campus Directory  Disability Resources  Emergency Information  Event Calendar  Job Openings  Library  Maps  UIC Safe Mobile App  UIC Today  UI Health  Veterans Affairs        Powered by Red 2.38.0  Â© 2020 The Board of Trustees of the University of Illinois |  Privacy Statement    Campuses   University of Illinois System  Urbana-Champaign  Springfield      Cookie Settings                 